36 years old today, no clue where time has gone. I remember 10 years ago I left my home in Chicago, everyone I knew drove all the way across country just to start a whole new life. I didn’t have any money not even $20. Point of the story is I literally felt like that was yesterday and time I just flying way to fast. BUT the best decision I have ever made in my 36 years of life was to move to Arizona. Arizona changed me forever, I pursued my dreams here. The city embraced it and I was able to finally live out my passion and do what I do because I love doing it. Last night was an epic night here in AZ and I love everyone that came out to support it. I started out the first day of 36 years of life with HISTORY being made in AZ. 
#IM36 💙
